# RSDFT
SYStype 1                         / SYStype ( 0:RSSOL, 1:RSMOL )
XCtype 'LDAPZ81'                  / Exchange-Correlation functional
PP 2 'C_psv.dat'                  / format and name of pseudopotential
scfconv 1.d-20                    / scf-convergence criterion
PROCS  2 2 4 1 1 1                / process partioning
Diter 100                         / Diter ( Max. # of iteration for SCF )
Nsweep  20                        / Nsweep ( Max # of iteration for Sweep )
IC  0                             / Input Control
OC  0                             / Output Control
ETLIMIT  1.d10                    / etime_limit
INFOLEVEL  1                      / info_level
SWSCF  1                          / scf

SWOPT  0                          / opt
ATOMOPT1  0  6  5                        / ncycl, most, nrfr
ATOMOPT2  0.5d0  1.d-10  1.d-8  1.d-1    / okatom, eeps, feps, decr
ATOMOPT3  100

